race.description: Douglass Blinds & Security Screens Mdn Plate
race.comment: YOU COUNT (5) is free-running and is ready to deliver off his two placed efforts this preparation. Has the blinkers on for the first time, and Heywood stays aboard. Will get every chance from an inside barrier. KOSRAE (9) debuts, and his two provincial trials have been sharp. Jumps from the paint and is thrown in with the 4kg claim. The yard is going well, and a bold run is likely. EMPRESS IRENE (6) had trialled well but didn't get into it off a sticky barrier at Wyong on debut. Collett stays aboard, and that's a push for his chances. Quick improvement is likely. STAKEHOLDER (3) decuts for Cairon Maher and just missed in the recent Kembla Grange trial. Has to be kept safe. FLYING GISELLE (7) debuts and was only beaten 1.9L in he latest trial at Warwick Farm. Draws to advantage, and she can race well.
